How to build ggl with autoconf/automake
=======================================
0. Pre-requirement
You need following packages installed before building ggl:
autoconf >= 2.59
automake >= 1.9.6
libtool >= 1.5.22

1. Initialize autoconf/automake
Run autotools/bootstrap.sh.
In project's root directory (where you found this INSTALL file), run
autotools/bootstrap.sh

2. Configure and build
Run utils/build_debug_ac.sh to build debug version. utils/build_release_ac.sh
is for release version.
